          "value": "DYNAMOOSBQA (10.238.80.140) PRD: DYSOAP1 (10.242.57.3) DYSOAP2 (10.242.57.4) DYSOAP3 (10.242.57.5) DYSOAP4 (10.242.57.6)"
        },
